<div class="post-footer">December 7th, 2009 |  Category: <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/copyleft/" title="View all posts in copyleft" rel="category tag">copyleft</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/copywrong/" title="View all posts in copywrong" rel="category tag">copywrong</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/free-culture/" title="View all posts in Free Culture" rel="category tag">Free Culture</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/law/" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/publicity-bitch/" title="View all posts in Publicity Bitch" rel="category tag">Publicity Bitch</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/sita-sings-the-blues/" title="View all posts in Sita Sings the Blues" rel="category tag">Sita Sings the Blues</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/the-interwebs/" title="View all posts in the interwebs" rel="category tag">the interwebs</a> | <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2009/12/07/correction-again/#comments" class="comments-link"  title="Comment on Correction, again">2 comments</a> </div>
