		<div class="post-777 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-animation category-law" id="post-777">


<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2009/11/14/more-courtroom-drawings/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to More Courtroom Drawings">More Courtroom Drawings</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p>This one&#8217;s about the Grand Jury selection process.</p>
<p><object width="400" height="320" ><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="movie" value="http://www.facebook.com/v/203680432641" /><embed src="http://www.facebook.com/v/203680432641" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" width="400" height="320"></embed></object></p>
<p>This one&#8217;s about&#8230;it&#8217;s hard to say. It&#8217;s supposed to loop.</p>
<p><object width="360" height="400" ><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="movie" value="http://www.facebook.com/v/203723407641" /><embed src="http://www.facebook.com/v/203723407641" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" width="360" height="400"></embed></object></p>
